resources.string:
The frighteningly funky and fearsome Freak returns, more powerful than ever! And this action-packed issue features the
gorgeous art of Barry Kitson - fresh from Marvels THE ORDER! Plus: Menace! Curt Connors! Aunt May! Lots of innocent bystanders! Gale wrote it, Wacker edited it, and Marvel actually thought it was a good idea to publish it!
Rated A ...$2.99
